{"tid":1395233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[恐怖紀錄] 730 葵涌黑警發癲 X 731 天水圍暴徒煙花突襲懶人包片上線","createTime":"2019-08-01T16:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T14:30:50.000Z","uid":1806,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bbaab80cec891366935db8462b6097496f7cb805","tid":1395233,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zrSFSgjucdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzrSFSgjucdk&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=db615296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zrSFSgjucdk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>今次我地團隊整左8分鐘半懶人包短片，簡述左7月30日葵涌警察濫用暴力同埋有名警察用槍指各人群事件，和7月31日凌晨狂徒駕車向人群放煙花後逃去，做成天水圍警署外多人受傷既經過。</strong><br />\n<br />\n已中英對照，歡迎share去外國。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>Credit to design 巴絲</em><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsc2gYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftsc2gYB.jpg&h=08fbf95d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>五大訴求<br />\n1. 徹底撤回《逃犯條例》修訂草案<br />\n2. 收回對6月12日衝突的「暴動」定性<br />\n3. 撤銷檢控及控罪並釋放被捕示威者<br />\n4. 追究警方濫用武力及權力（開槍發射橡膠子彈、布袋彈；濫發催淚彈）, 成立獨立調查委員會徹查所有事件<br />\n5. 重啟政改，實施「雙普選」（立法會選舉及特首選舉）, 解散立法會並立即重選, 行政長官林鄭月娥辭職下台</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8.5 三罷 7區集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong>"},{"pid":"a92de8eef18aa7f8da95aa6bd42be17c7ad7527d","tid":1395233,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d729a0ceb5be2dd3cb6fa4c8902b3732b0c7b17","tid":1395233,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988db735ca5b15dd261c8d274adc5363c1e29c01","tid":1395233,"uid":6038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955be9123156d7a42a3904d446fb50c3f11beece","tid":1395233,"uid":212156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:34:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4e605e1757418a8933df9661290e8fe82f3acb06","tid":1395233,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"955be9123156d7a42a3904d446fb50c3f11beece","tid":1395233,"uid":212156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:34:06.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92c1a965b55b2b797ec16a03da533e3035cfdb3","tid":1395233,"uid":6038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0927edd01e6e7d9e16cc1ed8f02fcdea6cead5e0","tid":1395233,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"